WEBVTT

00:01:59.744 --> 00:02:02.855
And what do stay-at-home moms
do all day, anyway?"

00:02:02.879 --> 00:02:06.117
Audience: Ooh!

00:02:06.141 --> 00:02:10.378
She smiled at me a smile
only a woman full of knowledge can smile

00:02:10.402 --> 00:02:11.744
(Laughter)

00:02:11.768 --> 00:02:14.633
and said, "Well, this
should be easy for you.

00:02:14.657 --> 00:02:17.482
And it will save us some money,
it seems like a no-brainer."

00:02:17.506 --> 00:02:18.551
(Laughter)

00:02:18.575 --> 00:02:20.204
Fast-forward six months,

00:02:20.228 --> 00:02:22.440
I'd been a stay-at-home dad
for about a week.

00:02:22.464 --> 00:02:23.696
(Laughter)

00:02:23.720 --> 00:02:27.061
I was standing in my bathroom,
looking into the mirror

00:02:27.085 --> 00:02:28.656
(Laughter)

00:02:28.680 --> 00:02:29.831
crying, tears --

00:02:29.855 --> 00:02:31.648
(Laughter)